fields.name: Original
fields.description: Come try our delicious original bread, made with the highest quality ingredients and baked to perfection by our skilled pastry chefs. Our bread is sure to become a new favorite in your home or business.

fields.name: Croissant
fields.description: Experience the rich, buttery goodness of our artisanal croissants, made by our team of skilled pastry chefs. These delectable treats are perfect for any occasion and will surely satisfy even the most discerning palates.

fields.name: Cream
fields.description: Indulge in the luxurious taste of our cream breads, made with creamy fillings and the highest quality ingredients. These delectable treats are a must-try for anyone who loves a little extra indulgence in their baked goods.

fields.name: Extra Coffe
fields.description: Our bread coffee is a unique and delicious blend of freshly baked bread and premium coffee beans, creating a one-of-a-kind flavor experience. This tasty treat is perfect for any coffee lover looking to switch up their routine and try something new

fields.name: Costro
fields.description: Cone Strawberry. Indulge in the sweet, fruity goodness of our strawberry ice cream cone. Made with the freshest ingredients and served in a crispy waffle cone, it's a treat that is sure to satisfy your cravings and bring a smile to your face.

fields.name: Vaco
fields.description: Vanilla Choco. Satisfy your sweet tooth with our rich and creamy choco vanilla ice cream. The perfect blend of chocolate and vanilla flavors makes it a delicious choice for any occasion.

fields.name: Oreo
fields.description: Experience the perfect blend of creamy vanilla ice cream and crunchy, chocolatey oreo cookies with our oreo vanilla ice cream. It's a classic flavor combination that never disappoints.

fields.name: Blue Fantasy
fields.description: Add a pop of color to your dessert menu with our colorful sprinkle-covered donuts. The fluffy, fresh dough and sweet glaze provide the perfect canvas for a generous helping of vibrant sprinkles, making these donuts a treat that is both tasty and eye-catching.

fields.name: Choco Volcano
fields.description: Molten chocolate cake is a dessert that consists of a chocolate cake with a liquid chocolate core. It is named for that molten center. And it is also known as chocolate coulant chocolate lava cake, or simply lava cake. It should not be confused with chocolate fondant, a recipe that contains little flour, but much chocolate and butter, hence melting on the palate (but not on the plate).

fields.name: Red Dream
fields.description: A cupcake is a small cake designed to serve one person, which may be baked in a small thin paper or aluminum cup. As with larger cakes, frosting and other cake decorations such as fruit and candy may be applied. For you, we give you special red velvet on red dream cupcake

fields.name: Misu
fields.description: Tiramisu in a glass, with honey, and fruits toppings, with smooth and fluffy cream gonna make your mood up

fields.name: Latte
fields.description: Latte , often shortened to just latte in English, is a coffee beverage of Italian origin made with espresso and steamed milk. Variants include the chocolate-flavored mocha or replacing the coffee with another beverage base such as masala chai (spiced Indian tea), mate, matcha, turmeric or rooibos; alternatives to milk, such as soy milk or almond milk, are also used.

fields.name: Moccacino
fields.description: is a chocolate-flavoured warm beverage that is a variant of a coffe latte commonly served in a glass rather than a mug. Other commonly used spellings are mochaccino and also mochachino. The name is derived from the city of Mocha, Yemen, which was one of the centres of early coffee trade. Like latte, the name is commonly shortened to just mocha.

fields.name: Expresso
fields.description: is a coffee-brewing method of Italian origin, in which a small amount of nearly boiling water (about 90 �C or 190 �F) is forced under 9�10 bars (900�1,000 kPa; 130�150 psi) of pressure through finely-ground coffee beans. Espresso can be made with a wide variety of coffee beans and roast degrees.

fields.name: Goldva
fields.description: Add a touch of glamour to your dessert menu with our Gold Vanilla donut. The fluffy, vanilla-flavored glaze is accented with a sprinkle of gold dust, making it a unique and indulgent treat that is sure to be a hit with any crowd

fields.name: Chocolato
fields.description: Our Chocolate donuts are a chocolate lover's paradise. The fluffy, fresh dough is coated in a thick layer of rich chocolate glaze, making them a decadent and satisfying treat. Whether you're in the mood for a sweet breakfast or a mid-day snack, these donuts are sure to hit the spot.
